        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo was the last robot gardener on the planet.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 2.625
            },
            {
              "text": "The world had become a dry, grey place after the great wars.",
              "audioStart": 3.487,
              "audioEnd": 6.875
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo walked across the empty land every day.",
              "audioStart": 7.737,
              "audioEnd": 10.175
            },
            {
              "text": "He searched for life, but he found nothing for many years.",
              "audioStart": 11.037,
              "audioEnd": 14.213
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "One afternoon, Leo noticed a small, green thing near a rock.",
              "audioStart": 15.075,
              "audioEnd": 18.663
            },
            {
              "text": "It was a tiny flower which was trying to grow in the dust.",
              "audioStart": 19.525,
              "audioEnd": 22.525
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo felt a new sense of hope when he saw the plant.",
              "audioStart": 23.387,
              "audioEnd": 26.012
            },
            {
              "text": "He knew that he must protect it from the harsh sun.",
              "audioStart": 26.875,
              "audioEnd": 29.262
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The robot carefully moved the plant into a glass container.",
              "audioStart": 30.125,
              "audioEnd": 33.15
            },
            {
              "text": "If he had not found it, the flower would have died.",
              "audioStart": 34.013,
              "audioEnd": 36.6
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo shared his own water with the little plant every day.",
              "audioStart": 37.462,
              "audioEnd": 40.325
            },
            {
              "text": "He watched it grow while he sat beside it in the quiet night.",
              "audioStart": 41.188,
              "audioEnd": 44.212
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "However, Leo had a problem because his battery was getting low.",
              "audioStart": 45.075,
              "audioEnd": 48.45
            },
            {
              "text": "His internal system indicated that he only had a few hours left.",
              "audioStart": 49.312,
              "audioEnd": 52.812
            },
            {
              "text": "He wanted to find a way to save the flower before he stopped.",
              "audioStart": 53.675,
              "audioEnd": 56.675
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo searched his memory for a solution to provide energy.",
              "audioStart": 57.538,
              "audioEnd": 60.562
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He realized that a solar panel could be connected to the glass jar.",
              "audioStart": 61.425,
              "audioEnd": 64.975
            },
            {
              "text": "If the sun hit the panel, the flower would receive enough light.",
              "audioStart": 65.838,
              "audioEnd": 69.05
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo moved the plant to a high place where the sun was strong.",
              "audioStart": 69.912,
              "audioEnd": 72.912
            },
            {
              "text": "He felt tired, but he was happy because the flower was safe.",
              "audioStart": 73.775,
              "audioEnd": 77.138
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The robot sat down and watched the light touch the green leaves.",
              "audioStart": 78,
              "audioEnd": 81.287
            },
            {
              "text": "He knew that his work was finally done.",
              "audioStart": 82.15,
              "audioEnd": 84.15
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo closed his eyes as his power went down to zero.",
              "audioStart": 85.013,
              "audioEnd": 87.862
            },
            {
              "text": "The flower continued to grow because the robot had saved it.",
              "audioStart": 88.725,
              "audioEnd": 91.85
            }
          ]
